morpho.name: Morpho Market V1 (Morpho Blue)
morpho.description: Main lending protocol contract. Enables supply/withdraw, borrow/repay, collateral management, liquidations, and zero-fee flash loans.

keyEvents.name: Supply
keyEvents.signature: Supply(bytes32 indexed id, address indexed caller, address indexed onBehalf, uint256 assets, uint256 shares)
keyEvents.description: Emitted when assets are supplied to a market

keyEvents.name: Withdraw
keyEvents.signature: Withdraw(bytes32 indexed id, address caller, address indexed onBehalf, address indexed receiver, uint256 assets, uint256 shares)
keyEvents.description: Emitted when assets are withdrawn from a market

keyEvents.name: Borrow
keyEvents.signature: Borrow(bytes32 indexed id, address caller, address indexed onBehalf, address indexed receiver, uint256 assets, uint256 shares)
keyEvents.description: Emitted when assets are borrowed from a market

keyEvents.name: Repay
keyEvents.signature: Repay(bytes32 indexed id, address indexed caller, address indexed onBehalf, uint256 assets, uint256 shares)
keyEvents.description: Emitted when borrowed assets are repaid

keyEvents.name: Liquidate
keyEvents.description: Emitted when a position is liquidated

useCases: Track user deposits and withdrawals by market
Monitor borrow/repay activity with accrued interest
Index liquidation events with collateral seized
Analyze market creation and parameter choices

adaptiveCurveIrm.name: Adaptive Curve Interest Rate Model
adaptiveCurveIrm.description: Morpho's flagship immutable IRM that autonomously adapts to market conditions

keyEvents.name: BorrowRateUpdate
keyEvents.description: Emitted when borrow rate is updated

useCases: Track interest rate changes across markets over time
Monitor rateAtTarget shifts and adaptation speed

bundler.name: Bundler (Bundler3)
bundler.description: Call dispatcher enabling atomic execution of multiple protocol interactions in a single transaction

keyEvents.name: Multicall
keyEvents.description: Emitted when multiple calls are batched

useCases: Track bundled transaction patterns and sequences
Measure gas savings vs unbundled transactions
